â€¢	Logistics: staffing plan â†’ vendor tasks â†’ signage/BOM â†’ runâ€‘ofâ€‘show â†’ incident runbooks.
â€¢	Postâ€‘event: NPS & session ratings â†’ budget reconciliation â†’ postmortem report with insights.
Data model (PostgreSQL + pgvector highlights):
â€¢	tenants, users, roles, api_keys, oauth_connections
â€¢	events(id, tenant_id, brief_json, city, venue_pref, start/end, status)
â€¢	venues(id, event_id, name, capacity, rooms[], cost_cards jsonb), rooms(id, venue_id, name, seats, features[])
